reviews.review_text:
Thanks for the memories ... the last time I have fond memories of this show as it was the last time my crew and I got to see Mr. Mydland.  I remember the music being great and Ramble On Rose in this recording is so sweet with Jerry & Brent taking us on a sweet journey.  

With Eyes to open (back in the day when there was a format) we knew we were in for a ride and the boys did not disappoint including treating us to a rare double encore to send us on our merry way.
